OL,5, Two LGBTQ artworks created in response 
OL,6, to hate crimes have been vandalised    
OL,7, within days of them being installed.   
OL,9,FThe pieces, created in reaction to a   
OL,10,Frecent spate of homophobic attacks in  
OL,11,FLiverpool city centre, were found      
OL,12,Fdestroyed on Friday and Tuesday.       
OL,14,FThe exhibition's organiser Homotopia   
OL,15,Fsaid it was "devastated" by the acts.  
OL,17,FMerseyside Police said the force had   
OL,18,Fbeen alerted to the first incident of  
OL,19,Fcriminal damage, which it was treating 
OL,20,Fas a hate crime.                       
